dct_title_s: A plan of the land of Canaan and the distribution of it according to Ezekiel's vision
dct_description_sm: Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Shows topography, drainage, boundaries, settlements, places of historical interest.
Includes index: Shewing the prince of Israels portion and that of the Levites.
Features an illustration of a compass rose.
Plan and distribution of the Holy Land divided among the twelve tribes of Israel on both sides of the Jordan River according to Ezekiel's vision.
